Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: We talk about overcoming adversity, we talked about addiction, and these are things that are never really hot topics. However as we create more safe places to have healthy conversations, it encourages a healthy environment to grow. If we equip ourselves and prepare to have certain conversations, they're healthier & happier. Dealing with Mental health doesn't need to be ominous or scary.
